flowchart LR
    HTTP[HTTP / WebSocket adapters] --> APP[Application use cases]
    ACTOR[Room actor] --> APP
    APP --> ENGINE[Deterministic engine]
    ENGINE --> DOMAIN[Domain state + rules]
    APP --> PORTS[Persistence / clock / random ports]
    PG[PostgreSQL adapter] --> PORTS
    REDIS[Redis adapter] --> PORTS
    CRYPTO[Crypto random adapter] --> PORTS
    ENGINE -. no infrastructure imports .- DOMAIN
